-- ============================================================
-- Korakuen Management System — Fix views security invoker
-- Migration: 007 (supersedes migration 004)
-- Date: 2026-03-01
-- Recreates all views with security_invoker = on
--
-- Note: Migration 006 was skipped — this migration was
-- originally numbered 006 but was regenerated as 007.
--
-- SOURCE OF TRUTH: supabase/views/*.sql
-- This migration was generated by combining the individual
-- view files. To update views, edit the source files in
-- supabase/views/ and create a new migration.
